# Reproducible local caches and autonomous research traces are not deployment
# inputs. Keeping them out of the upload reduces deploy time and prevents
# internal run history from reaching production bundles.
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/.DS_Store
**/tsconfig.tsbuildinfo
hasan-deploy/
research/raw/
research/audit_reports/
research/cost_reports/
config/ui_ux_memory/iteration_notes/
